OL,3,CMum's distress over young daughter
OL,4,C'locked inside' her own body
OL,6,FThe family of an 11-year-old girl from
OL,7,FKent is calling for better awareness
OL,8,Ffor children with a rare neurological
OL,9,Fcondition that leaves them "locked
OL,10,Finside" their own bodies.
OL,12,FPoppy Allard from Folkestone was born
OL,13,Fseemingly healthy.
OL,15,FBut her behaviour suddenly changed.
OL,17,FShe lost the use of her hands and
OL,18,Fstopped making noises.
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@GO]
