OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776427866
OL,3,CMum's distress over young daughter
OL,4,C'locked inside' her own body
OL,6,FPoppy was diagnosed with Rett syndrome
OL,7,F- which impacts brain development,
OL,8,Fleading to severe disabilities.
OL,10,FIt means she can't walk, talk or use
OL,11,Fher hands. Inside, Poppy is present,
OL,12,Fintelligent and emotional - using
OL,13,Fintense eye pointing to communicate.
OL,15,FPoppy also needs spinal surgery this
OL,16,Fyear and a lot of extra support. So
OL,17,Fher family's trying to build a
OL,18,Fsuitable space for her carers and
OL,19,Fmedical equipment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
