FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776427866
OL,3,CMum's distress over young daughter
OL,4,C'locked inside' her own body
OL,6,FThey've been in talks with Folkestone
OL,7,Fand Hythe District Council who say
OL,8,Fthey're committed to helping the
OL,9,Ffamily to meet their needs.
OL,11,FIn the meantime Poppy's Aunt and Uncle
OL,12,Fare running the Manchester marathon to
OL,13,Fraise money for Reverse Rett - a
OL,14,Fcharity set up by parents of children
OL,15,Fwith the condition.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
