OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776427866
OL,3,CMum's distress over young daughter
OL,4,C'locked inside' her own body
OL,6,FA Folkestone & Hythe District Council
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We have worked
OL,8,Fwith the applicant in trying to meet
OL,9,Ftheir needs while complying with local
OL,10,Fand national planning policy and
OL,11,Fguidance.
OL,13,F"That is a difficult balance to
OL,14,Fachieve but we remain committed to
OL,15,Ffinding an appropriate solution.
OL,17,F"Meanwhile, an application for a
OL,18,Fcertificate of lawful proposed use/
OL,19,Fdevelopment for a mobile home is
OL,20,Fcurrently being considered."
